---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Global Mobility & Residence Permits | ARM Management"
  description="UAE Golden Visa, EU investor residency, citizenship by investment, and international mobility solutions across 20+ countries."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530521954074-e64f6810b32d?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Global Mobility</span>
      <h1>Global Mobility &amp;<br>Residence Permits</h1>
      <p>Investor residency, work permits, and citizenship advisory across 20+ countries.</p>
      <div class="btn-row" style="justify-content:flex-start;margin-top:30px">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Speak With a Senior Advisor →</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn-secondary">Explore Our Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">What We Do</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Freedom of Movement as a Strategic Asset</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">For internationally mobile investors, entrepreneurs, and professionals, the ability to live, work, and travel freely across key markets is a fundamental strategic asset. The right residency or citizenship programme can transform your personal and commercial options — providing visa-free travel, stable legal residence, access to banking, and a credible second home jurisdiction.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">ARM Management advises across more than 20 countries, managing residency applications from document preparation and government submissions through to collection and post-approval support. We handle the process; you retain focus on your business.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Our Services</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Programmes We Advise On</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>UAE Golden Visa</h3>
          <p>All categories: investor (real estate AED 2M+), entrepreneur, talented professional, and exceptional talent. Document preparation, medical coordination, and Emirates ID processing handled end-to-end.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>EU Golden Visa Programmes</h3>
          <p>Investor residency across Greece, Portugal, Malta, Spain, and other EU member states — providing full Schengen area access and EU residency rights for investors and their families.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Investor &amp; Entrepreneur Visas</h3>
          <p>Structuring and applications for key jurisdictions including UAE, UK, Singapore, and selected EU member states. Entity formation coordinated with visa requirements where needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>Company-Sponsored Work Permits</h3>
          <p>Work permits and residency visas for relocated employees across multiple jurisdictions — including employer registration, quota management, and dependent visa coordination.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Family Member Inclusion</h3>
          <p>Extending residency rights to spouses, children, and dependants through simultaneous coordinated applications, ensuring the whole family travels on a single programme.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Citizenship by Investment</h3>
          <p>Second passport advisory across Malta, Turkey, Vanuatu, St Kitts and Nevis, and other programmes. Programme selection, due diligence preparation, and end-to-end application management.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--navy">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#B8960C">The ARM Approach</span>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="color:#F7F3EC">Residency Aligned to Your Life.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.78)">There are hundreds of residency and citizenship programmes available globally. The right one depends on your nationality, tax position, travel requirements, business interests, family situation, and long-term goals. ARM Management begins every mobility engagement with a thorough assessment — not a product recommendation. We advise on what will genuinely work for your specific situation, including the programmes we recommend against and the hidden costs many advisors omit.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:32px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Programme Fit Assessment</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">We assess which programme fits your situation before recommending one. Not every client needs a golden visa. Some need a work permit. Some need nothing but correct advice.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Tax Coordination</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Changing residency has tax consequences. We coordinate with your tax advisors — or our network — to ensure your new residency enhances your position, not complicates it.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Document Management</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Government applications require extensive documentation — apostilled, translated, and submitted in precise order. We manage the entire document chain on your behalf.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Post-Approval Support</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Residency programmes have ongoing obligations — renewal timelines, physical presence requirements, investment maintenance. We track these and notify you before deadlines arise.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Jurisdictions</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Where We Advise</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="reveal" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:32px">
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">UAE &amp; GCC</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">UAE Golden Visa (all categories), UAE residence visas, free zone and mainland employment visas.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">European Union</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Greece, Portugal, Malta, Spain golden visas. EU citizenship by naturalisation advisory. Schengen residency planning.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">Asia Pacific</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Singapore EntrePass and Employment Pass. Hong Kong talent and residency schemes. Malaysia MM2H.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">Citizenship Programmes</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Malta, Turkey, Vanuatu, St Kitts &amp; Nevis, Grenada, and others. Second passport advisory and application management.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Related Guides</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Go Deeper</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <a class="card reveal" href="/insights/uae-golden-visa" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">UAE</span>
          <h3>The UAE Golden Visa</h3>
          <p>Ten-year residency routes, current thresholds (AED 2M and the AED 30k salaried route) and the application process.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read the guide →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" href="/insights" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">All Insights</span>
          <h3>Browse the Guide Library</h3>
          <p>Jurisdiction and regulatory guides across the markets ARM advises in — reviewed and cited.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">View all →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Discuss Your Mobility Requirements</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Tell us your nationality, where you are based, where you want to be, and what you need from a new residency. We will identify the right programme and manage the process.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
      <a href="/insights" class="btn-secondary">Read Our Insights</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={`{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "name": "Global Mobility & Residency", "serviceType": "Global Mobility & Residency", "description": "Investor residency, work permits and citizenship advisory.", "provider": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "ARM Management", "url": "https://arm-management.com"}, "areaServed": ["European Union", "GCC & Middle East", "Asia-Pacific", "Latin America"], "url": "https://arm-management.com/services/global-mobility"}`} />
</Base>
